  "title": "Regional Sales Manager – Oil & Gas [EL]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Develop and execute regional sales strategies to meet revenue and profitability goals.</p></li><li><p>Drive new business development and manage key accounts within the steel line pipe segment.</p></li><li><p>Lead major contract negotiations and ensure competitive pricing.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with technical and operations teams to deliver tailored solutions.</p></li><li><p>Track market trends, competitor activity, and provide strategic insights to management.</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales forecasts, performance reports, and pipeline updates.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all sales activities comply with safety, quality, and regulatory standards.</p></li><li><p>Travel across Southeast Asia (40–50%) to engage clients and support regional operations.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s degree in Engineering, Business, or related discipline.</p></li><li>8–10 years of relevant sales experience in steel line pipe or oil & gas-related products, with regional exposure.</li><li>Strong experience managing major accounts and complex sales cycles.</li><li>Good understanding of pipeline projects and oil & gas infrastructure requirements.</li></ul><p><br />We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
